    "description": "If you're a passionate Reservation Manager with drive and ambition, Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd in Visakhapatnam is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nZomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Zomato Restaurant Partners Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
